reviewText: Wow, what can I say...LOVE this season too!!! You know how sometimes, a show starts out strong and then gradually loses steam? Not the case here!!! LMFAO funny in Season 3! I cannot get enough of this show...It's addicting, like the "dope" Ricky grows! LOL!!! I cannot stress it enough: If you have NEVER seen any Trailer Park Boys anything...START WITH THE TV SERIES!!! Just try it, you will come over to the dark side! Lots of foul language, but in a feel-good kinda way....

reviewText: Seasons 2, 3 and 4 are really the best of this show. It's starting to fizzle a little, but here in season 3 it is at full stride. The genius in this show is the script. So well crafted. The boys are at their most hilarious and heartbreaking in this season. I would recommend this and all seasons of TPB.

reviewText: BEING A CANADAIN, THIS SHOW IS THE ONLY THING KEEPING T.V REAL. I SICK OF STUPID AMERICAN SHOWS ON THE AIR ALL THE TIME. EVERY AMERICAN SHOW IS A REDUNDANT STICOM/REALITY SHOW THAT IS ONLY GOOD TO FEED THE MINDS OF A MINDLESS NATION (LOOK AT THE PRESIDENT) TRAILER PARK BOYS IS THE ONLY GOOD SHOW ON THE AIR TODAY, GREAT WRITING, GREAT CHARACTERS, AND OF COURSE, ITS CANADIAN, WHICH HELPS ALOT. THE BEST SHOW ON T.V SINCE KIDS IN THE HALL. IM HAPPY TO LIVE IN A COUNTRY THAT STILL HAS ORIGIONALITY AND A SENSE OF HUMOR, AND IF YOU WANT TO CHECK IT OUT, GUARANTEED YOU WILL FALL IN LOVE WITH TRAILER LIFE!
